{"tid":1387261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依家根本個政府同班黑警係迫我地所有事都自行私了","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T15:20:16.000Z","uid":60662,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3352a9bdb46653e1304fd3ed4ae3225f061cf8aa","tid":1387261,"uid":60662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"廢老打人唔拉<br />\n黑警打人唔拉<br />\n黑社會打人唔拉<br />\n你講乜野政府都唔會理<br />\n而你地繼續交稅比上面班人<br />\n<br />\n既然佢地咁推動私了，咁我地一定會配合。<br />\n班人就係想打到我地驚，反正都會比人屈，我地就學佢地打到佢地驚"},{"pid":"79b256eae4be3d59ca78a05b805d91a3ca775403","tid":1387261,"uid":60662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:34:44.000Z","msg":"每年就係交稅呢班仆街<br />\n邊個打我地一拳，我地就每人打返佢十拳"},{"pid":"70da57c460c576fa4525c3906d51657348c5ffd1","tid":1387261,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"冷靜D先<br />\n呢D野<br />\n到運動全面失面先做都唔遲<br />\n君子報仇 十年未晚"},{"pid":"4c88ac131f428628cae829ecb3fb3f0445972bd6","tid":1387261,"uid":167340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70da57c460c576fa4525c3906d51657348c5ffd1","tid":1387261,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"冷靜D先<br />\n呢D野<br />\n到運動全面失面先做都唔遲<br />\n君子報仇 十年未晚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:41:36.000Z","msg":"仲冷靜D先?  你想俾人打十幾拳再捅你兩刀, 跟住你同佢講道理呀??"},{"pid":"0c32f5176a1ef1ea041c2409d597cd2223b52b9c","tid":1387261,"uid":271051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"一早話左要私了啦<br />\n革命不是請食飯<br />\n睇下安重根"},{"pid":"6652480232aa35d279867fb41b60e77de11061b5","tid":1387261,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj